OL,3,CWhy learning to count is key to
OL,4,CHolyrood's assisted dying bill
OL,6,FIt's a cliche but in this case it's
OL,7,Falso true: MSPs are debating a matter
OL,8,Fof life and death.
OL,10,FLiam McArthur's Assisted Dying for
OL,11,FTerminally Ill Adults (Scotland) Bill
OL,12,Fhas members at Holyrood exercising
OL,13,Ftheir brains and their consciences as
OL,14,Fthey this week consider more than 320
OL,15,Famendments to the legislation.
OL,17,FThen there is the small matter of how
OL,18,Fto vote next Tuesday evening when the
OL,19,Ffinal decision is scheduled to be made.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
