PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1773349948
OL,3,CWhy learning to count is key to
OL,4,CHolyrood's assisted dying bill
OL,6,FThis is the furthest any bid to
OL,7,Flegalise the NHS helping someone with
OL,8,Fa terminal illness to end their life
OL,9,Fhas progressed through the Scottish
OL,10,Fparliament.
OL,12,FAttempts by Margo MacDonald and
OL,13,FPatrick Harvie in 2010 and 2015 both
OL,14,Ffell at the first vote while a 2004
OL,15,Fmotion by Jeremy Purvis, now Lord
OL,16,FPurvis of Tweed, failed to gain enough
OL,17,Fsignatures to even make it to the
OL,18,Ffloor of the parliament.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1773349948
OL,3,CWhy learning to count is key to
OL,4,CHolyrood's assisted dying bill
OL,6,FOne of the reasons this has progressed
OL,7,Fis the calm and respectful way
OL,8,FMcArthur has approached the proposals.
OL,10,FBut the momentum he built last year
OL,11,Fappears to be draining away from his
OL,12,Fproposals.
OL,14,FExchanges about amendments have been
OL,15,Fwell-tempered and well-informed in
OL,16,Fwhat is a free vote for MSPs, meaning
OL,17,Fthey are not bound by the whip of
OL,18,Ftheir leadership.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
