FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1773349948
OL,3,CWhy learning to count is key to
OL,4,CHolyrood's assisted dying bill
OL,6,FIt has provided a reminder of what
OL,7,FHolyrood can be when MSPs are not just
OL,8,Freading a speech typed for them by
OL,9,Fparty apparatchiks.
OL,11,FHowever, there appear to be areas
OL,12,Fwhere concerns cannot be alleviated no
OL,13,Fmatter how much is changed.
OL,15,FScottish Conservative leader Russell
OL,16,FFindlay, Holyrood's criminal justice
OL,17,Fcommittee convener Audrey Nicoll and
OL,18,Fher fellow SNP MSP Collette Stevenson
OL,19,Fhave each reversed their support.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1773349948
OL,3,CWhy learning to count is key to
OL,4,CHolyrood's assisted dying bill
OL,6,FAll three cited concerns that there
OL,7,Fare not enough protections to stop
OL,8,Fvulnerable people being coerced into
OL,9,Fsigning up to an assisted death.
OL,11,FOther worries centre on opt-outs for
OL,12,Fhealthcare workers who conscientiously
OL,13,Fobject to carrying out the procedures,
OL,14,Fgiven employment law is reserved to
OL,15,Fthe UK government.
OL,17,FMcArthur says that safeguards are
OL,18,Falready in the bill and work is
OL,19,Funderway between Holyrood and
OL,20,FWestminster to ensure that where
OL,21,Fpowers lie does not become an issue.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1773349948
OL,3,CWhy learning to count is key to
OL,4,CHolyrood's assisted dying bill
OL,6,FThe previous parliamentary vote passed
OL,7,Fwith a majority of 14. This means
OL,8,Fthose opposed to the legislation
OL,9,Fneeded to switch eight people to block
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,FSouth Scotland MSP Colin Smyth is not
OL,13,Fallowed into the building because of
OL,14,Fongoing criminal proceedings so cannot
OL,15,Fvote.
OL,17,FThat brings the number of required
OL,18,Fswitchers down to seven and three have
OL,19,Falready shifted.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1773349948
OL,3,CWhy learning to count is key to
OL,4,CHolyrood's assisted dying bill
OL,6,FWill Findlay's shift have any
OL,7,Finfluence over swithering Tories?
OL,8,FRemember, first minister John Swinney
OL,9,Fand Scottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,10,Falso oppose the proposal.
OL,12,FCan those like South Scotland MSP
OL,13,FBrian Whittle who backed the bill at
OL,14,Fstage one with huge reservations be
OL,15,Fpersuaded to overcome their concerns
OL,16,Fand stay the course?
OL,18,FThe mood music is not positive from
OL,19,FMcArthur's perspective.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1773349948
OL,3,CWhy learning to count is key to
OL,4,CHolyrood's assisted dying bill
OL,6,FThat's why we'll end with another
OL,7,Fpolitical cliche, one that despite its
OL,8,Foft-repeated use is just as important
OL,9,Fas the welcome high level debates
OL,10,Fcurrently taking place at Holyrood.
OL,12,FFormer US president Lyndon B Johnson
OL,13,Fsaid the first rule of politics is to
OL,14,Flearn to count.
OL,16,FAny summary of the numbers currently
OL,17,Fshow the bid to legalise assisted
OL,18,Fdying in Scotland is hanging by a
OL,19,Fthread.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
